Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Video Song | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the video song of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

Goddess Mahalakshmi, the deity of wealth and divine grace, is especially worshipped on Fridays (Shukravaram). Listening to her devotional songs on this sacred day is believed to attract prosperity, peace, and happiness into your life.

This video features the soulful bhakti song "Raavamma Mahalakshmi" along with other Friday-special devotional songs in Telugu, perfect for your daily or weekly pooja.

🌸 Why Listen on Fridays?

Invokes Mahalakshmi’s blessings for financial growth

Helps bring peace and harmony to the home

Removes negativity and spiritual obstacles

Ideal for Friday poojas, Lakshmi vratam, and daily bhakti

🎧 Use this during morning or evening prayers, especially on Fridays and auspicious days.

👉 Don’t forget to Subscribe to our channel for more devotional content, bhakti songs, and stotrams in Telugu.

🙏 Om Shreem Mahalakshmyai Namaha 🙏

Get ready to immerse yourself in the soulful melody of "Chokher Neele", the official video from the new Bengali movie Raktabeej 2, presented by Windows Production. This beautifully composed track captures the emotional depth and intrigue that lies at the heart of the movie’s narrative. With stunning visuals, powerful performances, and a hauntingly melodic score, Chokher Neele promises to be more than just a song — it’s an experience that stays with you.

As the sequel to the gripping Bengali thriller Raktabeej, this track sets the tone for what’s to come in the film’s storyline — filled with mystery, emotion, and cinematic brilliance. Don't miss the chance to witness the magic of Chokher Neele — a musical masterpiece that blends heart-touching lyrics with mesmerizing visuals.

snippet.title: Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song | Rakshakudu | Nagarjuna, Sushmita Sen | A.R. Rahman |Udit Narayan
snippet.description:
Listen & Enjoy the Melodious Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song from Rakshakudu Movie. Featuring Nagarjuna & Sushmita Sen, with Music by A.R. Rahman. Sung by Udit Narayan, P. Unnikrishnan & Harini, Lyrics by Bhuvanachandra, and Directed by Praveen Gandhi.

Song Details:
Song Name: Soniya Soniya
Singers: P. Unnikrishnan, Udit Narayan, Harini
Lyrics: Bhuvanachandra
Music Director: A.R. Rahman

Movie Details:
Movie Name: Rakshakudu
Banner: J.R.S. Combines
Producer: J. Rama Chandra Rao
Director: Praveen Gandhi
Audio On: Aditya Music.

Soniya Soniya Song Telugu Lyrics:

సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా ఆఆ
సోనియా సోనియా స్వీటు స్వీటు సోనియా రేగుతోంది లేత వయసు జోరు  
ఘాటు లవ్వు  రెండు టైపు నీటుదొకటి  నాటుదొకటి
రెండిట్లో ఏది నీకు ప్యారు
Sometimes  నీటే స్వీటు… Sometimes నాటే రైటు…
పిల్ల కళ్ళని చూసీ చేసేయ్ గురువా ఫైటు   || సోనియా|| 2
పువ్వుల్ని తడిమే చిరుగాలి మల్లె చెక్కిళ్ళు తడితే అది నీటు
కొమ్మల్ని విరిచే సుడిగాలి మల్లె ఒడి చేర్చుకుంటే అది నాటు
పచ్చిక మీద పడే చినుకుల మల్లె చిరు ముద్దులు పెట్టి శృతి చేయడమే నీటు
కసిగా మీద పడే ఉప్పన్నమల్లే చెలి పైటని పట్టి చిత్తు చేయడమే నాటు
నీ కురుల మీద పువ్వుని నేనై మురిపించే ఆట ఆడించనా
మృదువైన ముద్దుల్లో సొగసే ఉందే మంచంలో మాటలకి చోటేముందే
మత్తెక్కి కౌగిట్లో ముంచేస్తా అమ్మడు || సోనియా||
 
ఊరించే ఒడిలో  ఉపొంగే తడిలో బుగల్ని ఎంచక్కా పిండేస్తుంటే
పరువాల పిలుపే కళ్ళలో మెరుపై గుండెల్లో సెగలే రగిలిస్తుంటే
కౌగిలి క్రికెట్కి సిస్టమ్ లేదే అంపైరు లేడే మగతనముంటే చాలే
పట్టి పడతోస్తే వేగేదెట్టా బరువాపేదెట్టా ఎద మల్లెలపూవానోయ్
నలిపైకపోతే అందం లేదే కసి లేని మొహం మొహం కాదే
కోమలితో వాదిస్తే అర్ధం ఉందా కవ్వించి కాటేస్తే న్యాయం ఉందా
ప్రేయసిని గెలిచేది నా చూపుతానమేగా 
||సోనియా||

snippet.title: శుక్రవారం లక్ష్మీదేవి పాటలు🎶 | సౌభాగ్య లక్ష్మి రావమ్మా | Friday Special Lakshmi Devi Bhakti Songs
snippet.description:
శుక్రవారం లక్ష్మీదేవి పాటలు🎶 | సౌభాగ్య లక్ష్మి రావమ్మా | Friday Special Lakshmi Devi Bhakti Songs Telugu 

Goddess Lakshmi, the symbol of wealth, prosperity, and divine grace, is especially worshipped on Fridays. Listening to devotional songs on this day is believed to attract peace, abundance, and positive energy into your home.

In this video, enjoy the beautiful Telugu bhakti song "Sowbhagya Lakshmi Raavamma", specially sung to please Goddess Lakshmi and invite her blessings.

🌺 Why listen on Friday (Shukravaram)?

Brings financial stability and prosperity

Invites divine feminine energy into your life

Enhances mental peace and household harmony

Ideal for Friday Lakshmi puja or daily spiritual practice

🎧 Use this song during morning or evening prayer to elevate your devotion and connect with the divine energy of Sri Mahalakshmi.

👉 Subscribe for more Telugu bhakti songs and spiritual content every week!

🙏 Om Shreem Mahalakshmiyei Namaha 🙏


#LakshmiDeviSongs #FridaySpecialSongs #ShukravaramBhakti #TeluguBhaktiSongs #SowbhagyaLakshmi #MahalakshmiSongs #DevotionalSongsTelugu

snippet.title: Akshay Kumar, Nupur Sanon - Filhall (8K Lyric Video) |  BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Ammy Virk
snippet.description:
#jaani  #filhall #akshaykumar #bpraak  
Have you ever selflessly loved someone so much that just their smile can brighten up your day? 

FILHALL, a feel good song about love and it’s beauty of never giving up. 

From the makers of iconic songs like Qismat , Maan Bhariya , Pachtaoge  and Coka , one of bollywood most celebrated Artist Akshay Kumar  Featuring Nupur sanon , bring to you, their first ever debut Music video , in the voice of Bpraak . The video , shot is done by the concept king Arvindr Khaira  and penned down by one and only lyrical machine JAANI . Filhaal, a song that depicts the story of that true love which is pious, selfless yet incomplete. 

Desi Melodies proudly presents FILHALL  In association with cape of Good films & Azeem Dayani

snippet.title: Franklin & Shinchan Celebrate Onam with Maveli 🏆 Mammootty & Mohanlal in GTA 5 Malayalam
snippet.description:
✨ Happy Onam to everyone! 🌼
In this Onam Special GTA 5 Malayalam video, Franklin, Shinchan, and friends celebrate Onam with Mahabali, Mammootty, and Mohanlal. From Onasadya feasts to Onam games like KSRTC bus race, food eating challenge, and boat race, the fun never stops! 🎉

👉 Watch Franklin & Shinchan’s team win the Onam challenges and receive a grand gift of 10 villas from Mahabali before he returns to Paatalam. This Onam is full of laughter, challenges, and family celebrations.

🔥 Don’t miss this festive episode packed with comedy, action, and surprises!

#OnamSpecial #GTA5Malayalam #FranklinAndShinchan #Mammootty #Mohanlal #Mahabali

snippet.title: सांसो की माला पे सिमरु मैं शिव का नाम - Sejal Keshari - Sanso Ki Mala - Shiv Bhajan - Bhakti Song
snippet.description:
सांसो की माला पे सिमरु मैं शिव का नाम - Sejal Keshari - Sanso Ki Mala - Shiv Bhajan - Bhakti Song 

#sansokimala  #SejalKeshari #BhaktiGangasagar
​
► Song Credit:
► Song: Sanso Ki Mala Pe Simru Main Shiv Ka Naam
► Singer: 
► Lyrics: Traditional
► Music: 
► Mix & Master: 
► Music Label: Bhakti Ganga sagar
► Producer: 
► Video & GFX :

♪ Also Available on ♪
Spotify: 
Apple Music: 
Wynk:  
Gaana: 
Jio Saavn:
Amazon Prime Music: 
Youtube Music:  
Instagram: 
 Shazam: 
 

►Lyrics

सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम,
अब तो दुनियादारी से है,
मेरा क्या काम....

शिव के रंग में ऐसी डूबा,
बन गया एक ही रूप,
शिव की माला जपते जपते,
हो गयी सुबह श्याम,
सांसो की माला पे.....

शिवजी मेरे दिल में बसे है,
संग रहे दिन रात,
अपने मन की मै जानू ,
सब के मन की राम,
सांसो की माला पे....

शिवजी मेरे अंतरयामी,
शिवजी मेरे स्वामी,
शिवजी के चरणों में अर्पण,
ये जीवन तमाम,
सांसो की माला पे....

प्रेम पियाला जबसे पिया है,
जी का है ये हाल,
अंगारों पे नींद आ जाए,
और कांटो पे आराम,
सांसो की माला पे....

सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम,
अब तो दुनियादारी से है,
मेरा क्या काम,
सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम.....

सांसो की माला पे.....

शिवजी मेरे दिल में बसे है,
संग रहे दिन रात,
अपने मन की मै जानू ,
सब के मन की राम,
सांसो की माला पे....

शिवजी मेरे अंतरयामी,
शिवजी मेरे स्वामी,
शिवजी के चरणों में अर्पण,
ये जीवन तमाम,
सांसो की माला पे....

प्रेम पियाला जबसे पिया है,
जी का है ये हाल,
अंगारों पे नींद आ जाए,
और कांटो पे आराम,
सांसो की माला पे....

सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम,
अब तो दुनियादारी से है,
मेरा क्या काम,
सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम.....

snippet.title: Sheesha (HD Video) Sabba | Meavin | In Flow (EP) New Punjabi Songs 2025 | Latest Punjabi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
One Take Worldwide Presents

Song - Sheesha
Singer - SABBA
EP - In Flow 
Lyrics & Composer - Sabba
Music - Meavin
Producer - Meeru
Artwork - Garry Nawab
Label - One Take Worldwide

Lyrics :

Mai surma ne paaya,
Tu tareef kari akkhan di.
Shaapan challe laa teh,
Tu tareef kari hathan di.
Laune haar teh shingar bhi mai chaddteh ve,
Gena gatta chakkya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai ✨ (x2)
Haye jeenu jeenu keha tu balona b mai chaddya,
Oh ni suit paya jeda tenu naiyo fabbya.
Haye tere piche kinna kuj chad ke bethi aan,
Haye tu he mainu kite chadd javin na ve sabbeya.
Tenu bahr ne pasand jana mera,
Karon per pattya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai  (x2)
Hayee samne bethake mainu vendha rahe gaur naal,
Teh kahen is mukh nu makeup di b lorh na.
Vadh jeh gram audhon khoon mutiyar da ve,
Jadon kahe tere yahi dunia teh haur na.
Lagg nazar jave na saddi yaari nu,
Sehliyan nu dassya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai  (x2)

snippet.description:
Official music video for Visuvasam by Stella Ramola and Daniel Davidson.

Guitars - Franklin Simon

If you’re interested in music or video production and marketing services, kindly email stedansmusicroom@gmail.com

Lyrics:
Orupodhum visuvasathai vittuvidaadheergal
(Never let go of the faith)
Neengal visuvasithaal ellam koodumae 
(If you believe, everything will be possible)

Kadugalavu visuvasam irundhale podhum
(If you have mustard-seed sized faith,)
Yengugindra kaariyangal ellamae aagum
(Whatever you long for will happen)

Siricha mugamai varuvaaru
(With a smiling face, He will come)
Sirandhadhai ellamai tharuvaaru
(He will give you the best of everything)

1. Yobuvin vaazhkaiyai pola 
(Like the life of Job,)
Pala vidha (pala pala) kashtangal soola 
(In the midst of many kinds of trouble,)
Soraamal kartharai nee pidithukondal
(If you hold on to the Lord without growing weary,)

Yobuvin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Job’s blessing belongs to you)
Ilanthadhai irandu madangaai petrukondu
(You will get back whatever you have lost in double measure)
Ini sezhipaaga nee vazhndhidu
(From now on, you will live prosperously)

2. Kulandhaiyin selvathirkaaga 
(For the gift of child,)
Yaengidum saaraalaaga 
(Longing like Sarah,)
Pala naatkal kaathirundhu azhugindraaiyo
(Have you been tearfully waiting many days?)

Abraghamin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Abraham’s blessing belongs to you)
Naalaanaalum nichaiyamaaga mudivu undu 
(Even though it takes time, surely there is an end)
Un nambikkai veen pogaadhu
(Your hope will not be cut off)

℗ 2025 Stella Ramola

#StellaRamola #DanielDavidson #TamilChristianSong #SteDan #Visuvasam #MustardSeedFaith #NewTamilChristianSong #TamilChristianSong2025 #SteDansMusicRoom

snippet.description:
वीरवार स्पेशल  | Vishnu Ji Ke Bhajan | विष्णु जी के भजन |Ekadashi Bhajan | Hari Ke Bhajan | Bhajan

तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

रचा है सृष्टि को जिस प्रभु ने
श्री मन नारायण नारायण हरि 
मेरा छोटा सा परिवार हरि 
हरि नाम न ह्रदय से भूलों
हर सांस मे हो सुमिरन तेरा
श्री विष्णु अमृतवाणी
भगवान मेरी नैया उस पार लगा 
श्री  विष्णु जी के 108 नाम
ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय 
सत्यनारायण जी की आरती

⭐Singer : Upasana Mehta & Sanchit 
⭐Lyrics :  Archana Agarwa & Sachin Tulsiyan &Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)

snippet.title: নাচবে মনে ঢাকের কাঠি  🔱 Nachbe Mone Dhaker Kathi 😉 Durga Puja Song l Ariyoshi l Ft.Sandy l 2025 l
snippet.description:
নাচবে মনে ঢাকের কাঠি l Nachbe Mone Dhaker Kathi l Durga Puja New Song l Official Song l Ariyoshi Synthia l Sandy Rong l 2025 l 

Song Credits:
———————————-
Singer: Ariyoshi Synthia….
Lyrics: Bethun bera….
Composer: Apu Debnath…. 
Starring: Ariyoshi, Sandy Rong….
Music & Recording: Apu's Studio ….
Keyboard Programing: Hrishikesh banerjee 
Guitar: Kanai Singha….
Bass Guitar: Monoj Ghosh….
Mandolin: Subrata Majumdar… 
Mixing & Mastering: Apu debnath (Apu's Studio)….
Makeup and Hair: Amit Jana….
Assist: Koushik….
Costume and Jwellery: Tithitusar Series….
Choreography and Direction: Rishi Roy Chowdhury….
Assist: Aditya and Khushbu….
Cinematography: Tapas Das….
Assist:
Studio Partner : AP Studio (Suman)….
Team Managed By: Abhik Ghosh….
Special Thanks: Debayan, Sumana, Anupama, Angsu Avi, Ganesh, Mahadev….
————————————-



Song Lyrics:
———————————————

এবার পুজো হোকনা অন্যরকম,
তুমি আমি মেলি দুজন পেখম,
উড়ে উড়ে বেড়াই শুধু  চলো,
করবে না কেউ আমাদের ফলো,

শিউলি ফুলের গন্ধ মেখে
নেশাতে মাতাল হবো,
শরৎ মেঘের পিঠে চড়ে
খুশির দেশেতে যাবো।

কাশের বনে তুমি আমি
করবো দুজন প্রেম,
নাচবে মনে ঢাকের কাঠি
জমবে এবার গেম।

#

ষষ্ঠী থেকে দেখবো ঠাকুর
রাত্রি জাগা স্টার্ট,
সপ্তমীতে সাজবো এমন
লাগবে হেভি স্মার্ট।

কানের দুলের ঝুমকো লতা
চোখের কাজল বলবে কথা,
তোমার সাথে তুলবো ছবি
বাঁধিয়ে নেব যে ফ্রেম।

কাশের বনে তুমি আমি
করবো দুজন প্রেম
নাচবে মনে ঢাকের কাঠি
জমবে এবার গেম

#

অষ্টমীর ওই অঞ্জলিতে
ছুঁড়বো তোমায় ফুল
নবমীতে ভিড়ের মাঝে
করবো মিষ্টি ভুল

ফুচকা খাবো ঘুরে ঘুরে 
দেখবো ঠাকুর শহর জুড়ে 
দশমীতে মাখবো সিঁদুর
কুরতা শাড়ি পড়বো সেম 

কাশের বনে তুমি আমি
করবো দুজন প্রেম
নাচবে মনে ঢাকের কাঠি
জমবে এবার গেম
————————————————-

THANKS FOR WATCHING AND KEEP SUPPORTING….


#ariyoshi 
#nachbemonedhakerkathi
#pujorgaan
#durgapujanewsong

snippet.title: Hello Hanji (Teaser) | Sabba | Jasmeen Akhtar | Dr Zeus | Tanya Chauhan | Latest Punjabi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Speed Records and Sarbjit Saroya present the official teaser of “Hello Hanji”, a vibrant new Punjabi track featuring Sabba and Jasmeen Akhtar. From the very first frame, the teaser hints at a high-energy track packed with catchy beats, playful chemistry, and eye-catching visuals. Sabba’s cool vibe blends effortlessly with Jasmeen Akhtar’s bold presence, setting the tone for a fun, flirty, and full-on Punjabi banger.

The teaser gives just a taste—but it's enough to get fans excited for what’s coming. Whether you're into upbeat romance or dance-floor-ready music, Hello Hanji looks set to deliver both in style.

Credits:
Title: Hanuman Chalisa
Singer: Dipan Mitra
Music Director: Pamela Jain
Music Arrangements & Programming: Vijay Nanda
Flute: Sandeep Kulkarni
Rhythm Arrangement: Kunal Mohite
Mixing And Mastering: Aradhya Production (Mumbai)
Edit & Gfx: Prem Graphics PG
Music Label: Music Nova

Lyrics:
শ্রীগুরু চরণ পদ্ম স্মরি মনে মনে। 
Shreeguru Charan Padma Shmari Mane Mane

কোটি কোটি প্রণমিনু তাঁহার চরণে।। 
Koti Koti Pranaminu Tahar Charane

শ্রীরামের চরণপদ্ম করিয়া স্মরণ।
Shreeramer Charanpadma Koriya Shmaran

চতুর্বর্গ ফল যাহে লভি অনুক্ষণ।। 
Chaturbarg Phal Yahe Labhi Anukshan

বুদ্ধিহীন জনে ওহে পবন কুমার। 
Buddhihin Jane Ohe Pawan Kumar

ঘুচাও মনের যত ক্লেশ ও বিকার।। 
Ghuchao Maner Joto Klesh O Bikar

জয় হনুমান জ্ঞান গুণের সাগর।
Jai Hanuman Gyan Guner Shagar

জয় হে কপীশ প্রভু কৃপার সাগর।। 
Jai He Kapeesh Prabhu Kripar Shagar

শ্রীরামের দূত অতুলিত বলধাম। 
Shreeramer Doot Atulit Baldham

অঞ্জনার পুত্র পবনসুত নাম।। ১ ।।
Anjanar Putra Pavanshut Naam 

মহাবীর বজরঙ্গী তুমি হনুমান। 
Mahaveer Bajrangi Tumi Hanuman

কুমতি নাশিয়া কর সুমতি প্রদান।।
Kumati Nashiya Karo Shumati Pradaan

কাঞ্চন বরণ তব তুমি হে সুবেশ। 
Kanchan Baran Taba Tumi He Shubesh

কর্ণেতে কুণ্ডল শোভে কুঞ্চিত কেশ।।
Karnete Kundal Shobhe Kunchit Kesh

Hate Bajra Taba Aar Dhwaja Biraje
Shundar Gadaati Kandhe Tomar Shaaje
Aparup Bahu Taba Pawan Nandan
Mahatej O Prataap Jagat Bandan

Vidyabaan Gunbaan Tumi He Chatur
Shreeramchandrer Kaajye Tumi He Aatur
Sharboda Ramerat Korite Palan
Hridaye Rakho Shada Ram Shita O Lakhman

Shookshma Roop Dhori Tumi Lanka Probeshile
Dhoriya Bikat Roop Lanka Dagdha Koile
Bheem Roop Dhori Tumi Ashur Shanghar
Shreeramchandrer Tumi Sharb Kaaj Kor

Shanjeevan Ani Tumi Banchale Lakhman
Raghubeer Han Tahe Aanandit Man
Raghunath Dil Toma Alingan Daan
Kohilen Tumi Bhai Bharat Shamaan

Shahashra Badan Taba Gabe Jash Khyati
Ei Boli Alingan Koren Shripati
Shanakadi Brahmadi Jotek Devgan
Narad Sharad Adi Dev Rishigan

Yam O Kuber Adi Dikpal Gane
Kobi O Kobid Joto Ache Tribhubane
Shugriver Upokar Tumi Je Korile
Ramshaho Milaiya Rajpad Dile

Tomar Mantrona Shob Bibhishon Manil
Lankeshorer Bhoye Shob Kompoman Chhil
Shahashra Yojon Urdhe Shuryadebe Dekhe
Shumadhur Phal Boli Dhayile Grashite

Jai Ram Boli Tumi Ashim Shagar
Par Hoye Probeshile Lankar Bhitor
Durgom Jotok Kaaj Ache Tribhubane
Shugom Korile Tumi Shob Ram Gaae

Chir Dwari Acho Tumi Shreeramer Dware
Taba Kabina Keho Probeshite Nare
Sharan Loinu Prabhu Ami Je Tomari
Tumi Rakhak Mor Aar Kare Dori

Nij Tej Nije Tumi Koro Shomboron
Tomar Hunkare Dekh Kaape Tribhuvan
Bhoot Pret Pishaach Kachhe Ashite Na Pare
Mahaveer Taba Naam Jei Jon Shmare

Rog Nash Koro Aar Sharb Pira Hara
Mahaveer Naam Jeba Shmare Nirontor
Shankatete Hanuman Uddhar Korite
Tahar Charane Jeba Mon Pran Dibe

Sharbopori Ramchandra Tapashwi O Raja
Shreeramer Arigan Tumi Dile Shaja
Tomar Charane Jeba Mon Pran Dibe
Ei Jibone Sheijan Shada Shukh Pabe

Prabal Prataap Taba He Bayu Nandan
Char Jug Ujjwal Rahibe Tribhuvan
Shadhu Shanyashire Rakha Koro Matiman
Shreeramer Priya Tumi Ati Gunban

Ashta Shiddhi Naba Shiddhi Jaha Kichu Roy
Shokoli Shiddh Hoy Tomar Kripay
Ram Ramayan Achhe Taba Nikotei
Shreeramer Dash Hoye Royecho Shadai

Tomar Bhajan Koile Ramke Paibe
Janme Janme Tar Dukh Ghuch Jabe
Antokale Pabe Shei Ramer Charan
Ei Shar Kotha Shob Shun Bhaktagan

Shob Chhari Bolo Shobe Jai Hanuman
Hanumant Sharbashukh Koribe Pradaan
Sharb Dukh Dure Jabe Shankat Katibe
Jei Jon Hanumante Shmaran Koribe

Jai Jai Jai Jai Hanuman Goshai
Taba Kripa Binna Aar Kono Gati Nai
Jei Jon Shatobar Iha Path Kore
Shokal Ashanti Tar Chole Jaay Dure

Hanuman Chalisha Je Koren Pathon
Sharbakajje Shiddhi Labh Kore Shei Jon
Tulsidash Sharbodai Shree Harir Dash
Moner Mondire Prabhu Koro Shada Baash

Moner Mondire Prabhu Koro Shada Baash
